# content-allowlist — file paths where the content-pattern scan is SKIPPED.
# One POSIX extended regex per line. # for comments.
#
# Use for files where your name / copyright / contact info is EXPECTED.
# The blocked-paths check still runs normally; only the content scan is skipped.

# Open-source author attribution — your name is supposed to be here
(^|/)LICENSE(\.md|\.txt)?$
(^|/)COPYING(\.md|\.txt)?$
(^|/)NOTICE(\.md|\.txt)?$
(^|/)AUTHORS(\.md|\.txt)?$
(^|/)COPYRIGHT(\.md|\.txt)?$
